            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Iucunda <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> Tiberi <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>iberta</ex></expan> Felicis <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>nat</abbr><ex>u</ex></expan> XX et <lb n="4"/>Primio filius <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> VIII <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>unt</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Ancharius <lb n="7"/>Castus <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uo</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>posuit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Acht aneinanderpassende Fragmente. Z. 2: Felicis in kleineren Buchstaben in den Zwischenraum zwischen l(iberta) ann(orum) eingefügt. Z. 2, 4, 6: die letzten Buchstaben der jeweiligen Zeilen sind in den rechten Rand eingemeißelt. (B): Boppert: Z. 2: Feli(ci)s; AE 1979: Z. 3: natu.</p>
            </div>
